  <brief_title>PRF for Accelerating Palatal Healing</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Platelet-Rich Fibrin on Palatal Wound Healing After Free Gingival Graft Harvesting: A Comparative Randomized Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
